<html>
	<head>
		<title>BCM_GETTEXT</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
		<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>BCM_CLEARMARKER</strong></font></p>
		<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%" bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><pre>BCM_CLEARMARKER
	wParam = ( WPARAM )( int )nMarker;
	lParam = ( LPARAM )( int )nLine;</pre>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p>Clears&nbsp;the marker&nbsp;from the given line.</p>
		<ul>
			<ul type="disc">
				<li>
					Returns TRUE if the marker was actually&nbsp;cleared and FALSE if not.</li>
			</ul>
		</ul>
		<DL>
			<dt><em>nMarker</em>&nbsp;
				<DD>
					The marker to clear. This must be a number between 1 and 5. <DT><EM>nLine</EM>
						<DD>
							The line number to&nbsp;clear the marker from. This must be between 1 and the 
							number of lines in the text.</DD></DL>
	</body>
</html>
